  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Raptor</title>

    <para>Installez <application>Raptor</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

 <!-- patch -Np0 -i ../raptor-&raptor-version;-curl.patch &amp;&amp; -->

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

